frus:attachment.head:
The Belgian Minister for Foreign Affairs (
    Jaspar
) to the American Chargé (
    Wadsworth
)

frus:attachment.p:
Whereas on August 21, 1919, the Principal Allied
and Associated Powers unanimously accepted the accord concluded between the
British Empire and Belgium;

Thence, a straight line in a southerly direction to the north shore of Lake
                        Mohazi, where it terminates at the confluence of a river situated about 2.5
                        kilometers west of the confluence of the River Msilala;
